description: Realfiction Holding AB engages in the provision of mixed reality solutions for retail, education, events and brand activations. The company is headquartered in Helsingborg, Skane. The company went IPO on 2017-07-14. The firm uses the mixed reality technology, which blends reality with digital animations and information, and applies it to marketing products. The firm offers product line Dreamoc, which combines physical objects with holograms to create a three-dimensional (3D) content. Also, Dreamoc includes built-in audio, high-end glass optics and Content Management System. Another product is the DeepFrame, which is a mixed reality display that projects living images as a layer onto the real world in any size and over any distance, as well as uses filmed or 3D animated content in full colour and 4,000 pixels resolution.
